items.title: Awesome Micropython
items.content_text:
### Sensors / Camera

*   [micropython-camera-API (⭐95)](https://github.com/cnadler86/micropython-camera-API) - Project with the aim of supporting cameras across various ports in MicroPython, starting with the ESP32 port and Omnivision cameras (OV2640 & OV5640).
items.content_html:

  • micropython-camera-API (⭐95) - Project with the aim of supporting cameras across various ports in MicroPython, starting with the ESP32 port and Omnivision cameras (OV2640 & OV5640).
